<preface id="preface" xreflabel="preface">
<title>Preface</title>


<para>

The fftw Roll provides the fftw libraries for a Rocks cluster.
It installs the libraries in /opt/fftw/lib on both server and client hosts.
If the intel and/or pgi compilers are present, it also installs versions of
the fftw libraries compiled with those compilers.

</para>

</preface>
